What is Flutter?

Flutter is a UI toolkit For building Fast, Beautiful,Natively Compliled Application for mobile web and desktop 
with one programming language and single Codebase it was developed by google and Now Manages by an ECMA Standards .
Flutter Apps Uses dart Programming Language for creating an app 

Flutter Framework are Known as cross Platform Development tools. it has ability to write one code and can deploy on the various platfrom

Features Of Flutter:- 

1.Open-Source
2.Cross-platform
3.Hot Reload
4.Accessible Native Features and SDKs
5.Minimal code
6.Widgets

Flutter Mainly Optimized for 2D Mobile Apps That can Run Both Android and Ios Platfrom 

Flutter is a full-fledged SDK, it includes a rendering engine, ready-made widgets, testing and integration APIs, 
